<section class="ac-section-heading">
  <div>
    <p class="ac-eyebrow">Tag index</p>
    <h1>标签索引</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="ac-section-meta">用主题风格浏览所有标签</p>
</section>

<section class="ac-info-grid ac-info-grid-compact">
  <article class="ac-info-card">
    <span>标签总数</span>
    <strong><%= site.tags ? site.tags.length : 0 %></strong>
    <p>把主题、教程和项目笔记按关键词归档。</p>
  </article>
  <article class="ac-info-card">
    <span>文章总数</span>
    <strong><%= site.posts ? site.posts.length : 0 %></strong>
    <p>从 Obsidian 发布后，这里会自动汇总全部文章。</p>
  </article>
  <article class="ac-info-card">
    <span>浏览方式</span>
    <strong>按主题探索</strong>
    <p>适合先从感兴趣的方向切进去，再看对应文章。</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="ac-tag-index">
  <% if (site.tags && site.tags.length) { %>
    <% site.tags.each(function(tag){ %>
      <a class="ac-tag-cloud" href="<%- url_for(tag.path) %>">
        <span>#<%= tag.name %></span>
        <strong><%= tag.length %> 篇</strong>
      </a>
    <% }) %>
  <% } else { %>
    <div class="ac-empty-state">还没有标签。</div>
  <% } %>
</section>
